data.description: Well well... what do we have here! A cute, totally refreshed home in one of Piedmont's highly sought after neighborhoods waiting just for you! Upon entering you're greeted by the new vinyl plank flooring throughout, spacious living room with a fireplace and a large dining room. This unique floor plan is perfectly distributed! Two bedrooms on one wing with a full bath in between, the master retreat on the other side PLUS a bedroom with an en-suite tucked away in the other corner of the home that would be perfect for multigenerational living! Each bedroom has fresh carpet as well! The kitchen is presented with a modern flair including stainless steel appliances, rich charcoal grey cabinetry and brass accents! Outside you have plenty of room to roam! You'll also be getting a BRAND NEW ROOF! This home is equipped with ample space and storage you have to see it for yourself!! The neighborhood offers a pavilion, tennis and basketball courts and a large grassy field!
